<!-- ===== PAGE HERO ===== -->
<div class="page-hero">
  <div class="page-hero-bg"></div>
  <div class="page-hero-content">
    <div class="hero-two-col">
      <div>
        <div class="page-eyebrow">Performance Materials Lab &nbsp;|&nbsp; Teaching</div>
        <h1>Engineering<br><em>From the Inside</em><br>Out</h1>
        <p class="page-hero-sub">Two courses. One conviction: that students learn engineering best from someone who has spent decades doing it. Twenty-five years on factory floors, in boardrooms, and at startup launchpads is the curriculum that no textbook can provide.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="hero-philosophy">
        <p>The gap between theory and practice is not a flaw in engineering education. It is the subject.</p>
